  "title": "URGENT HIRE: Assistant Planning Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in the development and monitoring of project schedules in line with completion dates outlined in contracts.</li><li>Collaborate with project managers and engineering teams to ensure alignment of schedules with project objectives.</li><li>Prepare regular progress reports and updates to track project milestones and deadlines.</li><li>Analyze project performance data to identify potential scheduling issues and propose corrective actions.</li><li>Support the planning process by gathering necessary information and documentation for project schedules.</li><li>Communicate effectively with stakeholders to ensure clarity and understanding of project timelines.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering or Construction.</li><li>Proficient in Primavera P6 and Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Strong analytical and organizational skills.</li><li>Excellent communication and teamwork abilities.</li><li>Detail-oriented with a focus on accuracy in scheduling.</li><li>Ability to work effectively under tight deadlines.</li></ul><p>If interested, please submit your application to cvs@jdawms.com with your expected salary and resume.</p><p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly. By submitting your application or resume, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and sharing of your personal information with potential employers for their assessment.</p><p>JDA WMS Pte Ltd | EA Personnel: Pham Thi Tuyet Mai </p><p>EA License No: 23S1595 | EA Registration No: R25127838</p>",
